{"tid":1218925,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"《抗爭手語》","createTime":"2019-06-13T17:09:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-09T13:42:02.000Z","uid":63171,"like":17,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"0db0eb0cd0dc4eb79620ba997a527a5d4dd84f3d","tid":1218925,"uid":63171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T17:09:03.000Z","msg":"《抗爭手語》<br />\n抗爭手語有助遠距離溝通，對現場尤其前線防守非常重要。令物資得以從後方物資站，經由支援人士送到前線補給。<br />\n以下圖解近日常用物資手語如下：<br />\n<br />\n「頭盔」：<br />\n兩手掌放在頭部上方，上下晃動，模仿頭盔保護頭部。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XjJxV4E.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXjJxV4E.gif&h=248d1b3c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n「索帶」：<br />\n高舉雙手，以拇指及食指拉出一條水平的無形索帶。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kwfPYzi.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkwfPYzi.gif&h=68f7b01d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n「眼罩」：<br />\n雙手成C形，放在眼睛兩邊，模仿眼罩保護眼睛。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qDKUqen.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqDKUqen.gif&h=b43e66c2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n「口罩」：<br />\n雙手成C形，放在嘴巴兩邊。類似眼罩動作。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yEjM0NL.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyEjM0NL.gif&h=07df06a3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n「長遮」：<br />\n雙手上下握拳，在身前模仿雨傘撐開動作。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wkGSWmb.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwkGSWmb.gif&h=9b79f0b6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n「Marker」：<br />\n單手高舉，食指指天，模仿書寫動作。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kWcKNsV.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkWcKNsV.gif&h=fbc1a26c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n「哮喘藥」：<br />\n拇指向下，放在嘴邊，模仿吸用哮喘藥。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/FCxny7Y.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FFCxny7Y.gif&h=afd1d522&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n「保鮮紙」：<br />\n雙手握拳打圈，「火車捐山窿」，模仿保鮮紙包裹雙手。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/pnSrgmm.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FpnSrgmm.gif&h=1a44ff65&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n「生理鹽水」：<br />\n雙手模仿握罐，分別以順/逆時針轉動。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MQZM0N3.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMQZM0N3.gif&h=a042b478&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n「剪刀」：<br />\n單手比剪刀手，橫向剪出。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hu3U9Gr.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fhu3U9Gr.gif&h=8e0daf5b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n「剪鉗」：<br />\n高舉雙手，雙手分別展示剪刀手。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AwJBDzP.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAwJBDzP.gif&h=d4d7bb23&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n「六角匙」：<br />\n單手伸出拇指及尾指，六字手勢。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KUt2y8d.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKUt2y8d.gif&h=ba165761&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n「鐵馬」：<br />\n雙手大動作劃出拱門形狀。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Pi0Xn1F.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPi0Xn1F.gif&h=5dc30fe6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n「物資已足夠」：<br />\n雙手在胸前打交义。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6PymPGL.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6PymPGL.gif&h=3984529d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n*同一手語可能有超過一種表達形式，暫以小弟淺見作準，歡迎留言對《抗爭手語》提出意見。"},{"pid":"b585d92adc9b1b7f1fa7dea7de234c8f0fde2c13","tid":1218925,"uid":63171,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T17:11:51.000Z","msg":"一圖睇盡：<br />\ndownload有助隨時溝通<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BT9AUdr.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBT9AUdr.gif&h=7b099ad8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6c7c51384c36e6843b0c600c6f56ff8a14cf1084","tid":1218925,"uid":154486,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T19:07:34.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e3d596fa2275ebd7e7f358889b2149